Output demo/atom-httpie-demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1280
Set Height 900
Set Padding 18
Set TypingSpeed 45ms

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "cd /home/arvindh/absmach/atom"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "PATH=$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:18080 ADMIN_SECRET=change-me DEMO_STEP_SLEEP=4 ./demo/atom-httpie-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 230s
